182.09"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27174" id="p275_w6" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="182.09" base="190.01" width="123.006" height="9">むくっとベッドから起き上がる。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="90.596" height="9" id="p275_t7" x="48.264" y="199.13"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27176" id="p275_w7" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="199.13" base="207.05" width="90.596" height="9">「戻ってきたんだ……」</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="82.44" height="9" id="p275_t8" x="56.424" y="233.09"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27180" id="p275_w8" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="233.09" base="241.01" width="82.44" height="9">デカゲル時計を見る。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="47.52" height="8.1" id="p275_t9" x="56.544" y="250.13"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27183" id="p275_w9" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.544" y="251.903" base="258.05" width="8.58" height="8.1">11</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p275_s27184" id="p275_w10" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="66.624" y="250.13" base="258.05" width="9" height="9">月</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p275_s27185" id="p275_w11" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="76.944" y="251.903" base="258.05" width="8.46" height="8.1">30</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p275_s27186" id="p275_w12" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="86.904" y="250.13" base="258.05" width="17.16" height="9">日。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="58.8" height="9" id="p275_t10" x="48.264" y="267.05"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27188" id="p275_w13" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="267.05" base="274.97" width="58.8" height="9">「――え！？」</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="131.166" height="9" id="p275_t11" x="56.424" y="284.11"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27191" id="p275_w14" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="284.11" base="292.03" width="131.166" height="9">余韻が一気に吹っ飛んでしまった。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="66.12" height="9" id="p275_t12" x="56.424" y="318.07"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27195" id="p275_w15" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="318.07" base="325.99" width="66.12" height="9">どういうことだ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="196.475" height="9" id="p275_t13" x="56.424" y="335.11"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27198" id="p275_w16" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="335.11" base="343.03" width="196.475" height="9">私の誕生日。私がゕトラガに旅立った日ではないか。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="196.466" height="9" id="p275_t14" x="48.264" y="352.15"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27200" id="p275_w17" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="352.15" base="360.07" width="196.466" height="9">「まさか……夢ゝゴなんてことない……でしょうね」</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="66.12" height="9" id="p275_t15" x="56.424" y="369.07"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27203" id="p275_w18" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="369.07" base="376.99" width="66.12" height="9">エッと青ざめる。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="310.505" height="9" id="p275_t16" x="56.424" y="386.11"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27206" id="p275_w19" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="386.11" base="394.03" width="310.505" height="9">これまでの体験がすべて夢だったなんて……レ゗ンのこともゕルオ゚さんのこともす</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="220.946" height="9" id="p275_t17" x="48.264" y="403.18"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27207" id="p275_w20" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="403.18" base="411.1" width="220.946" height="9">べて夢だったなんて……そんなのは……そんなのは地獄だ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="106.802" height="9" id="p275_t18" x="56.424" y="437.14"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27211" id="p275_w21" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="437.14" base="445.06" width="106.802" height="9">ベッドから勢いよく降りる。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="131.166" height="9" id="p275_t19" x="56.424" y="454.18"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27214" id="p275_w22" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="454.18" base="462.1" width="131.166" height="9">その瞬間、バエっという音がした。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="66.84" height="10.035" id="p275_t20" x="56.544" y="470.875"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27217" id="p275_w23" font-name="Arial" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.544" y="470.875" base="479.02" width="66.84" height="10.035">――紫苑の書だ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="106.803" height="9" id="p275_t21" x="56.424" y="488.136"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27220" id="p275_w24" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="488.136" base="496.056" width="106.803" height="9">私は慌ててペーカを開いた。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="220.809" height="9" id="p275_t22" x="56.424" y="505.2"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27223" id="p275_w25" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="505.2" base="513.12" width="220.809" height="9">するとそこにはこれまでのすべてがきちんと記されていた。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="139.331" height="9" id="p275_t23" x="48.264" y="522.12"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27225" id="p275_w26" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="522.12" base="530.04" width="139.331" height="9">「よかった……夢じゃなかったのね」</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="74.28" height="9" id="p275_t24" x="56.424" y="539.16"><TOKEN sid="p275_s27228" id="p275_w27" font-name="ipa¾©" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="539.16" base="547.08" width="74.28" height="9">胸を撫で下ろした。</TOKEN></TEXT></PAGE>
